  "text": "All samples from each subject were analyzed on the same plate in duplicate. To reduce interference from plate biases, subjects were paired and balanced according to diet, fat distribution, insulin sensitivity index, and blood pressure parameters. Samples/subjects were balanced and paired using a space-filling design from a principle component analysis model calculated based on the subjects' baseline characteristics [CITATION_1] .",
